strings: <voice_0x01001C90><se_high>Media princess: Sorry, I'm a little busy and I miss Martha.
<voice_0x01001C92><se_high>Media princess: A very lonely woman recently died. You will never marry your true love
<voice_0x01001C93>Media princess: Ironically, I thought about my current situation.
<voice_0x01001C94><se_high>Media princess: (sigh) Fate is a strange thing...
